        <h1 style="text-align: center;"> ABOUT THE INSTITUTE</h1>
        <p>The M.I.E.T. Society, founded by Er. A. Mohamed Yunus during the year 1984, offers a high quality holistic education in an underdeveloped rural and semi-urban region of Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu. The societyâ€™s members include leading Industrialists, Educationists and Philanthropists.

            M.I.E.T. Engineering College was established by the Mohamed Institute of Education & Technology Society, Tiruchirappalli in the year 1998 with an objective to promote the cause of higher education. The College is affiliated to Anna University, Chennai. It is recognized as a Muslim Minority Institution.
            
            Our Management extends its fullest support in building the institution as a centre of excellence with technically superior, ethically strong and competent engineers. The serene campus vibrant with aesthetic bliss in an exhilarating convenient location, well connected by road, rail and air is easily accessible.</p>
